full_text: Screened by NARA, 8/7/2023 NOTICE OF ENTRY OF APPEARANCE AS ATTORNEY OR REPRESENTATIVE DATE In re: 03/03/95 SINGH, Jagat FILE No. I hereby enter my appearance as attorney for (or representative of), and at the request of, the following named person(s): NAME Petitioner Applicant SINGH Jagat Beneficiary ADDRESS (Apt.
